"Most customers really buy it for security reasons," adds Pilin.
In his opinion, however, the child should always know the purpose of the "box" and how to use it in an emergency.
However, the child psychologist Dana Bočková points out that if a child does not like to wear such a thing, it will simply get rid of him.
